let me interview you

283
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,920
about how you feel right now.

284
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:33,240
Xiong Yuanbao.

285
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:35,280
62.

286
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:37,640
Your score is a joke.

287
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:41,560
Why did you read it so loudly?

288
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,960
Am I wrong?

289
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,320
You didn't submit the essay,

290
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:45,720
and you almost failed.

291
00:14:45,800 --> 00:14:46,840
You study here every day,

292
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:48,480
but I don't know what you're actually learning.

293
00:14:48,480 --> 00:14:49,920
You're just putting on a show.

294
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:51,580
You got the semifinal notice.

295
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:52,840
Is that a big deal?

296
00:14:53,880 --> 00:14:54,810
What did you say?

297
00:14:56,880 --> 00:14:57,940
What are you doing?

298
00:14:58,520 --> 00:15:00,050
Are you trying to hit a girl?

299
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:09,320
Mu Qingyun, what are you doing?

300
00:15:14,160 --> 00:15:16,160
A real man doesn't fight with girls.

301
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,200
Look at your hair.

302
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:21,760
And you have the nerve to argue with a girl?

303
00:15:21,760 --> 00:15:22,690
I'm telling you,

304
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:24,120
get a haircut tomorrow.

305
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:25,640
Instant karma.

306
00:15:26,520 --> 00:15:27,320
Students,

307
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:29,320
don't learn from him.

308
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:32,220
All right, pack your things. School's over.

309
00:15:45,160 --> 00:15:46,520
Don't just think about studying.

310
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:48,560
Play a game and balance work and rest.

311
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:49,400
I won't play.

312
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:50,700
If you dare to play,

313
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:52,560
let's see if Auntie doesn't punish you when she gets back.

314
00:15:52,560 --> 00:15:54,120
If I wasn't completely sure,

315
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,450
how would I dare to play?

316
00:15:55,560 --> 00:15:56,960
If my mom catches me,

317
00:15:57,400 --> 00:15:58,960
she will definitely use lynching

318
00:15:58,960 --> 00:16:00,240
and skin me alive.

319
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:02,120
I really suspect that we were

320
00:16:02,160 --> 00:16:03,320
switched at the hospital when we were little.

321
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:04,400
My mom is your mom,

322
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:05,680
and your mom is my...

323
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:10,360
Sorry.

324
00:16:10,920 --> 00:16:12,640
I didn't mean to say that.

325
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:16,160
It's fine. I'll play with you for a bit.

326
00:16:16,600 --> 00:16:17,800
But let's make a deal,

327
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:20,000
don't get angry while playing the game.

328
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:20,960
Absolutely.

329
00:16:21,040 --> 00:16:22,480
Why get angry over a game?

330
00:16:22,560 --> 00:16:23,240
Go, go, go.

331
00:16:25,280 --> 00:16:26,540
We lost because of you.

332
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:27,840
Were you playing with your feet?

333
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:29,560
I told you not to get angry over a game.

334
00:16:29,560 --> 00:16:30,840
Plus, I'm a girl.

335
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:31,920
Who's angry?

336
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:33,400
Isn't it your fault? Tell me.

337
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:35,600
Mu Qingjun, you're still talking.

338
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,600
Who started it?

339
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:40,480
Him. Her.

340
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:43,290
Bring out the family rules.

341
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:47,080
Grandma. Grandma.

342
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,840
Don't look at Grandma. Look at me.

343
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:49,720
Let's begin.

344
00:17:05,599 --> 00:17:06,440
I've told you so many times

345
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:08,170
not to fight, but you still did.

346
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:09,839
How old are you?

347
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:11,319
Apologize.

348
00:17:12,079 --> 00:17:13,280
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

349
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:15,599
What are you waiting for? Start.

350
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:20,440
Because we are a family,

351
00:17:20,760 --> 00:17:23,839
a family that loves each other.

352
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:26,079
Fate brought us together.

353
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:27,880
Only with heart can we cherish.

354
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:31,040
Why let the dark clouds cover our eyes?

355
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:33,240
The results are out, right?

356
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:36,160
Yuanbao, 82 points.

357
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,200
Not bad at all.

358
00:17:37,320 --> 00:17:39,250
Qingyun, where is your test paper?

359
00:17:40,320 --> 00:17:41,560
Take it out.

360
00:17:46,560 --> 00:17:47,960
Hurry up. Stop dawdling.

361
00:17:58,560 --> 00:18:00,200
Forty-eight?

362
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:02,840
Look at you.

363
00:18:02,920 --> 00:18:05,200
You still have the nerve to play games with such low marks.

364
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:06,720
Your hair is so long, and you haven't cut it.

365
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:08,040
Your teacher already complained to me.

366
00:18:08,040 --> 00:18:09,370
Get a haircut right now.

367
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:11,120
I got it.

368
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:12,440
I won't play anymore.

369
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:13,760
I'll study hard.

370
00:18:13,880 --> 00:18:14,920
Study hard.

371
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:16,600
You used to have good grades when you were little.

372
00:18:16,600 --> 00:18:17,600
Look at you now.

373
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:19,480
Have you ever scored higher than Yuanbao?

374
00:18:19,480 --> 00:18:21,360
Do you think you are the Chinese national football team?

375
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:23,400
Consistently bad, aren't you? All day long...

376
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:24,660
I'll beat you to death.

377
00:18:31,480 --> 00:18:32,280
Yuanbao,

378
00:18:32,440 --> 00:18:34,240
your homeroom teacher called me

379
00:18:37,520 --> 00:18:40,380
and said this essay competition is very important.

380
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:43,040
She also praised your talent for writing.

381
00:18:46,920 --> 00:18:47,920
It scared me.

382
00:18:48,120 --> 00:18:50,380
I thought you two got into trouble again.

383
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,160
Yuanbao,

384
00:18:51,240 --> 00:18:53,280
when are you going to the competition?

385
00:18:53,280 --> 00:18:54,200
This Saturday.

386
00:18:54,320 --> 00:18:55,180
This Saturday?

387
00:18:55,560 --> 00:18:56,420
That's so soon.

388
00:18:58,320 --> 00:19:00,760
I have an event at the factory on Saturday.

389
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:02,940
Let your uncle go with you.

390
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:05,720
I... I have a job interview.

391
00:19:08,160 --> 00:19:10,200
Dad, you're going to a job interview?

392
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:11,440
No, no, no.

393
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:13,650
It's another better opportunity.

394
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:15,360
They insisted I go check it out

395
00:19:15,360 --> 00:19:16,960
and give them some guidance.

396
00:19:17,040 --> 00:19:19,480
It's fine. I'll go with Yuanbao.

397
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:20,880
Don't worry.

398
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:23,600
Grandma, I can go by myself.

399
00:19:23,840 --> 00:19:25,280
Big cities are very safe.

400
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:27,640
With your IQ,

401
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:29,560
if you go out alone...

402
00:19:30,440 --> 00:19:30,880
You!

403
00:19:31,440 --> 00:19:33,320
How dare you mock my IQ.

404
00:19:35,320 --> 00:19:36,400
These two kids.

405
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:38,440
If she goes out alone,

406
00:19:38,840 --> 00:19:42,100
she'd probably help count the money if she gets kidnapped.

407
00:19:42,360 --> 00:19:44,640
How about this? Let Qingjun go with Yuanbao.

408
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:45,760
They are grown up now.

409
00:19:45,760 --> 00:19:47,080
It's time for them to get some experience.

410
00:19:47,080 --> 00:19:47,680
Yes, get some experience.

411
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:48,840
That works.

412
00:19:48,960 --> 00:19:50,480
They can keep each other company

413
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:51,940
and look after each other.

414
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:52,920
Us two?

415
00:19:53,120 --> 00:19:54,800
No looking after each other,

416
00:19:55,120 --> 00:19:56,720
and no mutual progress.

417
00:19:56,800 --> 00:19:58,120
Only mutual disgust.

418
00:19:58,280 --> 00:19:59,440
Mutual sarcasm.

419
00:20:01,720 --> 00:20:03,180
You two are so articulate.

420
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:06,400
Alright, the Shanghai trip is settled.

421
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:08,360
Qingjun, when you're away from home,

422
00:20:08,360 --> 00:20:09,820
take good care of Yuanbao.

423
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:13,680
Mom, how much travel expenses

424
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:16,360
are you going to give us?

425
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:20,120
Five hundred.

426
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:21,280
No more than that.

427
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:24,660
Yuanbao, you manage the money. Don't give it to him.

428
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:27,400
Mom, only five hundred?

429
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:29,120
What can five hundred do?

430
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:31,160
Travel expenses, accommodation...

431
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:32,480
It'll all be gone.

432
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:35,440
Besides, Yuanbao eats so much.

433
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:37,600
I'm afraid she'll starve.

434
00:20:40,280 --> 00:20:41,840
Yuanbao, eat more meat.

435
00:20:53,280 --> 00:20:53,760
Aunt Ling.

436
00:20:53,760 --> 00:20:55,120
Yuanbao, studying?

437
00:21:04,880 --> 00:21:05,960
I have

438
00:21:06,160 --> 00:21:07,420
another 500 yuan here.

439
00:21:08,120 --> 00:21:09,280
Take it.

440
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:11,360
Also, during dinner today,

441
00:21:11,480 --> 00:21:13,360
judging by your uncle's reaction,

442
00:21:13,360 --> 00:21:15,320
I think he might give you money too.

443
00:21:16,240 --> 00:21:18,000
If that's the case,

444
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:19,520
I want to see

445
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:20,720
how much secret money

446
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,400
he has hidden from me.

447
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,060
In this matter,

448
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:25,640
you must take my side.

449
00:21:25,760 --> 00:21:26,720
Hear me?

450
00:21:31,120 --> 00:21:32,650
It's not easy being a woman.

451
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:40,400
Who is it?

452
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:42,440
Yuanbao, can I come in?

453
00:21:44,240 --> 00:21:47,240
Uncle, wait a second.

454
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:03,320
Uncle, why are you here?

455
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,200
Yuanbao, listen to me.

456
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:05,760
Come in.

457
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:07,120
Take a seat.

458
00:22:11,320 --> 00:22:12,320
Listen to me.

459
00:22:12,880 --> 00:22:13,920
While your aunt is

460
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:15,200
out buying soy sauce,

461
00:22:15,280 --> 00:22:16,120
I brought you

462
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:20,520
my secret savings.

463
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:23,760
Remember to buy some good food on the road.

464
00:22:24,080 --> 00:22:25,280
Travel comfortably,

465
00:22:25,360 --> 00:22:26,560
and don't mistreat yourself.

466
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:27,320
Hear me?

467
00:22:29,040 --> 00:22:30,640
What's wrong with your eyes?

468
00:22:31,440 --> 00:22:32,200
Take it.

469
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:33,560
Here's 600.

470
00:22:33,840 --> 00:22:35,280
I saved it for months.

471
00:22:36,760 --> 00:22:39,240
Spend it wisely.

472
00:22:39,600 --> 00:22:40,600
If there's any left,

473
00:22:40,600 --> 00:22:42,260
remember to give it back to me.

474
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:44,960
Don't tell your aunt.

475
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:47,040
It's not easy being a man.

476
00:22:49,480 --> 00:22:51,140
What's wrong with your mouth?

477
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:55,800
Your aunt must be back.

478
00:23:06,720 --> 00:23:07,720
Yuanbao.

479
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:11,360
Honey.

480
00:23:12,680 --> 00:23:13,680
Everyone's here.

481
00:23:15,560 --> 00:23:16,690
Aunt Wenying, Aunt.

482
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:18,520
You keep Yuanbao company.

483
00:23:18,760 --> 00:23:20,600
I'll go do some chores.

484
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:25,280
Auntie, Uncle.

485
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:29,600
What's going on?

486
00:23:31,000 --> 00:23:33,200
Let's go home. I'll deal with you later.

487
00:23:34,320 --> 00:23:35,560
Gently.

488
00:24:01,200 --> 00:24:03,930
This is the style Zhicheng's top guy should have.

489
00:24:04,240 --> 00:24:07,920
I am Mu of the Zang'ai Family.

490
00:24:14,680 --> 00:24:16,040
I'm going to school by myself today.

491
00:24:16,040 --> 00:24:17,440
Don't get too close to me.

492
00:24:26,000 --> 00:24:27,060
What is a disguise?

493
00:24:27,080 --> 00:24:28,200
This is a disguise.

494
00:24:28,720 --> 00:24:30,320
You can't even recognize me.

495
00:24:34,960 --> 00:24:35,840
Mutou.

496
00:24:39,280 --> 00:24:40,840
Come, solve this problem.

497
00:24:47,240 --> 00:24:48,760
Pass. Next.

498
00:24:49,200 --> 00:24:50,560
What do you mean 'pass'?

499
00:24:51,160 --> 00:24:52,440
Teacher, you forgot.

500
00:24:52,520 --> 00:24:53,480
You said before

501
00:24:53,560 --> 00:24:55,320
to quickly skip the questions we don't know

502
00:24:55,320 --> 00:24:56,800
to save everyone's time.

503
00:24:58,480 --> 00:25:00,000
Then there's nothing wrong with saying that.

504
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:00,920
Yuanbao.

505
00:25:11,880 --> 00:25:14,480
Xiong Yuanbao is reading a leisure book in class.

506
00:25:14,480 --> 00:25:16,800
Sorry, teacher. I was wrong.

507
00:25:23,800 --> 00:25:24,920
Mr. Tian.

508
00:25:26,280 --> 00:25:29,520
It seems my class isn't attractive enough.

509
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,800
Yuanbao finds it very boring.

510
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:33,400
She shared this with me.

511
00:25:33,960 --> 00:25:35,490
Now I'm sharing it with you.

512
00:25:37,680 --> 00:25:38,600
Class dismissed.

513
00:25:38,600 --> 00:25:39,320
Stand up.

514
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:43,600
Goodbye, teacher.

515
00:25:43,680 --> 00:25:44,740
Take care, Mr. Liu.

516
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:47,540
Xiong Yuanbao,

517
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:49,060
and Mu Qingjun,

518
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:51,320
come to my office.

519
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,960
Nothing good comes from arrogance.

520
00:25:55,080 --> 00:25:56,080
Fellow Daoist.

521
00:25:57,080 --> 00:25:58,000
Well.

522
00:25:58,320 --> 00:26:00,480
It bodes ill.

523
00:26:00,720 --> 00:26:02,400
It's fulfilled.

524
00:26:03,080 --> 00:26:03,960
Tough guy,

525
00:26:04,400 --> 00:26:05,000
take care.

526
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:06,320
Director,

527
00:26:06,600 --> 00:26:07,520
this is Xiong Yuanbao, who entered

528
00:26:07,520 --> 00:26:09,640
the re-examination of the New Concept.

529
00:26:09,640 --> 00:26:11,960
This child is usually very hardworking

530
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:13,800
and especially likes writing,

531
00:26:13,800 --> 00:26:18,160
particularly reading these world classics.

532
00:26:18,320 --> 00:26:19,240
Right?

533
00:26:21,280 --> 00:26:23,800
I do like reading world classics.

534
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:26,080
The younger generation is truly formidable.

535
00:26:26,080 --> 00:26:27,280
Our Zhicheng School

536
00:26:27,520 --> 00:26:29,250
has always been top in science,

537
00:26:29,560 --> 00:26:31,760
but relatively weaker in liberal arts.

538
00:26:32,080 --> 00:26:33,480
A New Concept contestant

539
00:26:33,520 --> 00:26:34,840
is a first for us.

540
00:26:35,080 --> 00:26:38,080
You must win glory for the school this time.

541
00:26:39,080 --> 00:26:39,880
Mr. Tian,

542
00:26:40,040 --> 00:26:41,640
if there's any need for tutoring in composition,

543
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:43,120
our school will fully support it.

544
00:26:43,120 --> 00:26:43,800
Okay, don't worry, Director.

545
00:26:43,800 --> 00:26:44,930
I'll leave you to it.

546
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:48,200
Mr. Men.

547
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:50,000
No, Mr. Tian.

548
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:52,280
Then about my world classic,

549
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:53,840
can I have it back?

550
00:26:53,840 --> 00:26:55,280
Don't even think about it.

551
00:26:55,280 --> 00:26:56,240
Xiong Yuanbao,

552
00:26:56,320 --> 00:26:58,850
Give you an inch and you take a mile, don't you?

553
00:26:59,040 --> 00:27:00,680
Did your parents send you to school

554
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:02,120
just to read these...

555
00:27:02,240 --> 00:27:03,680
idle books?

556
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:05,130
I'm telling you,

557
00:27:05,240 --> 00:27:07,640
focus on the competition and nothing else.

558
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,240
And you,

559
00:27:11,520 --> 00:27:12,440
Mu Qingyun.

560
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:14,240
What are you laughing at?

561
00:27:14,240 --> 00:27:15,570
You're only a freshman.

562
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:17,280
Look at your hair.

563
00:27:17,360 --> 00:27:18,920
Do you think you're a hedgehog?

564
00:27:18,920 --> 00:27:19,920
By the way, Yuanbao.

565
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:22,160
Since you made it to the New Concept Writing Competition semi-finals,

566
00:27:22,160 --> 00:27:23,640
about that essay about mothers,

567
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:25,080
when are you going to hand it in?

568
00:27:25,080 --> 00:27:26,720
I've urged you several times.

569
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:27,840
Everyone else has handed it in.

570
00:27:27,840 --> 00:27:29,640
I just urged you yesterday and you still haven't.

571
00:27:29,640 --> 00:27:31,240
Do you have a problem with me?

572
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:35,120
Xiong Yuanbao,

573
00:27:35,600 --> 00:27:37,200
Have you learned from Mu Qingyun

574
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,930
to always go against teachers?

575
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:42,120
I don't know how to write it.

576
00:27:42,120 --> 00:27:44,520
Yuanbao, what are you talking about?

577
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:46,140
What's wrong with you?

578
00:27:46,600 --> 00:27:48,530
Do you want me to call your parents?

579
00:27:52,280 --> 00:27:53,540
Don't call my parents.

580
00:27:54,600 --> 00:27:55,520
I'll write it.

581
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:57,880
Yuanbao.

582
00:28:12,280 --> 00:28:13,400
What happened?

583
00:28:15,120 --> 00:28:15,920
Mu Qingjun.

584
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:18,840
What's wrong with Xiong Yuanbao?

585
00:28:18,840 --> 00:28:20,280
No, I don't get it.

586
00:28:20,360 --> 00:28:22,760
It's just an essay. Is it really necessary?

587
00:28:23,080 --> 00:28:24,840
Don't you live opposite her house?

588
00:28:24,840 --> 00:28:25,720
Tell her

589
00:28:26,080 --> 00:28:27,610
I want to talk to her family.

590
00:28:30,080 --> 00:28:30,960
Mr. Tian.

591
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,080
Yuanbao,

592
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:36,080
she has her reasons.

593
00:28:41,880 --> 00:28:44,740
What's so great about getting a semi-final notice?

594
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:47,040
Got scolded, huh?

595
00:29:08,040 --> 00:29:09,120
Did you know?

596
00:29:09,320 --> 00:29:11,380
Xiong Yuanbao is actually an orphan.

597
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:12,960
An orphan?

598
00:29:13,800 --> 00:29:14,720
No way.

599
00:29:14,880 --> 00:29:15,680
It's true.

600
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:19,060
I heard Mu Qingyun telling the teacher with my own ears.

601
00:29:19,080 --> 00:29:20,080
Did you know?

602
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:21,240
Xiong Yuanbao's grandmother

603
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:23,120
works as a nanny at Mu Qingyun's house.

604
00:29:23,120 --> 00:29:24,840
I heard she's making money for her

605
00:29:24,840 --> 00:29:26,500
to cover her living expenses.

606
00:29:27,360 --> 00:29:28,560
No way, Zhicheng.

607
00:29:28,560 --> 00:29:28,960
No way.

608
00:29:29,520 --> 00:29:31,120
I heard about this a long time ago.

609
00:29:31,120 --> 00:29:33,050
The fireworks factory explosion.

610
00:29:33,120 --> 00:29:35,360
It seems it was due to a mistake.

611
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:36,800
I know.

612
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:38,080
My mom mentioned this to me.

613
00:29:38,080 --> 00:29:40,280
I think Yuanbao's parents...

614
00:29:40,520 --> 00:29:41,800
I'll leave the factory to you.

615
00:29:41,800 --> 00:29:42,520
Okay.

616
00:29:45,760 --> 00:29:47,420
I never expected the culprits

617
00:29:47,520 --> 00:29:49,280
to be Xiong Yuanbao's parents.

618
00:29:51,480 --> 00:29:52,440
Mom.

619
00:29:53,040 --> 00:29:53,880
Yuanbao.

620
00:29:55,440 --> 00:29:56,600
Mom promises you,

621
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:58,400
she'll be right back.

622
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:06,880
Really?

623
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:11,400
How many families did that ruin?

624
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:13,800
And they ended up dying themselves.
